{
  "stem": "20021.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I entered the train, the train was packed full, you could hardly move there, and I arrived in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was-- there was two kinds, people who had money and could use gold or diamonds or whatever and change it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A little gold went a long, long way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, if you sold something for a gram of gold, you got an awful lot of money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother would be selling from her jewelry, which she had quite a bit, because Jews generally believed in accumulating jewelery in-- in those years because of the tradition of having to run, starting from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The history was always full of all kinds of pograms and runnings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They developed the sense that they need to-- to hoard gold and dollars, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother had money, which you know, my father actually left it when he left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that helped her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you had money, you could buy food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a black market for everything, you see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Plus, the fact that my mother worked as a cook helped her also to get some provisions which she could bring home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was not hungry, not hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Clothes, you couldn't buy clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no new clothes available.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to live with your old clothes, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What about the role of the Judenrat?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Judenrat, it depends in which town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Basically, they were collaborators in a way, but you had to say-- you know, there is a big controversy of the issue of the Judenrat which I don't want to dwell in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you might have heard about Hannah Arendt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hanna Arendt was a philosopher, a renowned philosopher in the United States, a professor at Columbia and all that, many publications.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
